    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Dear Sirs;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "There currently are rumors over the grapevine and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "in print that suggest men with oriental features wearing dark clothes go",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "around terrorizing people who have had close-up views of UFO's.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "It is also rumored these creatures have impersonated armed forces officers",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "and FBI investigators. They are supposed to ride around in black or dark",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "automobiles that either have old licence tags or none at all. Several are",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "reported to have attempted to run down witnesses of UFO sightings, made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "disturbing almost macabre phone calls, silenced several investigators who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "were supposed to have learned some dark secret about extraterrestial craft",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "or mission plans and opened mail, tapped telephones and even taken pictures",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of several homes where UFO witnesses lived.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Can you give me any information on such rumors? Or can you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "refer me to a source whose facilities can answer my questions?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "this information will help settle some disturbing questions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "the readers of my articles. Personally I am not sure at all whether I can",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
